00:24:40,771 --> 00:24:44,086
ikh veys nisht far vos? ikh bin geven di shvakhste.

410
00:24:44,086 --> 00:24:46,946
SO zey hobn tsugenumen fun d- mir dem kufer.

411
00:24:46,946 --> 00:24:52,438
