417
00:25:11,946 --> 00:25:15,367
bin ikh nokh dem azoy fil tsores durkhgegangen,

418
00:25:15,367 --> 00:25:16,929
ikh, di shvakhe,

419
00:25:16,929 --> 00:25:23,665
vos ikh ken mir nisht gleybn az der tate hot gebroykht ts- tsutsu-, heysn tsunemen fun mir a valizkele.

420
00:25:23,665 --> 00:25:27,718
SO undz ze'mir ongekumen, m'hot undz ge-

421
00:25:27,718 --> 00:25:30,297
in di vagonen geleygt,

