00:25:30,297 --> 00:25:34,231
in Svalyave, un m'hot undz gefirt oyf Munkatsh.

423
00:25:33,122 --> 00:25:35,368
oyf di, in di vagonen oyf di tsug.

424
00:25:35,368 --> 00:25:37,369
oyfn tsug, tsu, gefirt tsu di s-

