00:25:40,403 --> 00:25:43,052
tsu forn, nor oyf, fun Svalyave tsu Munkatsh

428
00:25:43,052 --> 00:25:45,841
iz dos nor tsvey sho tsu forn.

429
00:25:45,841 --> 00:25:49,140
un m'hot undz gebrengt in tsigl fabrik.

430
00:25:49,140 --> 00:25:51,578
yeder, koydem,

431
00:25:51,578 --> 00:25:54,403
hot men gezogt shteln zikh in di reye,

432
00:25:54,403 --> 00:25:59,315
un yeder eyner zol opgebn vos m'hot gebrengt, vayl az nisht me vet

433
00:25:59,315 --> 00:26:02,069
bazukhn, un vemen me vet

434
00:26:02,069 --> 00:26:03,561
vos me trefn,

435
00:26:03,561 --> 00:26:06,999
vet men sh- h-, tomer vet men trefn bay emetsern

436
00:26:06,999 --> 00:26:09,069
vet men, vet men hargenen.

437
00:26:09,069 --> 00:26:11,455
me vet shisn, me vet shlogn.

438
00:26:11,455 --> 00:26:13,982
azoy vos yeder hot moyre gehat.

439
00:26:13,982 --> 00:26:18,578
un yeder hot opgegebn vos m'hot gebrengt.

440
00:26:18,578 --> 00:26:22,912
m'hot undz geheysn, in droysn iz gevezn shtroy.

441
00:26:22,912 --> 00:26:29,298
yeder zol zikh nemen a bintl shtroy un trefn a plats,

442
00:26:29,298 --> 00:26:31,403
oyfn boydem,

443
00:26:31,403 --> 00:26:35,631
