00:27:21,104 --> 00:27:23,385
m'hot aroysgefirt di mener.

456
00:27:23,385 --> 00:27:26,701
m'hot nisht gelozt shlofn. m'hot aroysgefirt di mener.

457
00:27:26,701 --> 00:27:28,621
un m'hot zey geheysn in di nakht,

458
00:27:28,621 --> 00:27:30,526
azoy vi di tate olevasholem,

459
00:27:30,526 --> 00:27:32,315
er iz nisht geven a gezunter.

