484
00:28:59,736 --> 00:29:08,262
SO dos, dos iz geven azolkhe shtiklekh, azolkhe vos zenen gekumen az di fashistn kukn.

485
00:29:08,262 --> 00:29:10,718
nokh dem iz gekumen a fashist,

486
00:29:10,718 --> 00:29:14,332
un heybt on tsu fregn ver vosere

487
00:29:14,332 --> 00:29:19,210
ayngeshtelte, vi zey hobn gemakht dos lebn, vi zey hobn gemakht...

488
00:29:19,210 --> 00:29:21,807
eyn mazl, der tate iz tsugekumen

489
00:29:21,807 --> 00:29:26,368
ven er hot mikh gefregt un hot gezogt "ikh ho- undz ho'mir gehat a shikh gesheft."

490
00:29:26,368 --> 00:29:30,228
